<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>BAWIPA JESUH, NANGMAH KAN ZUMH CH327</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa Jesuh nangmah kan zumh, Nangmah lawng kan zumh, Khamhnak tha na
 chim cangmi kha, Ka pe tuah.

[C1]
   Nang kan zumh ko, Nangmah lawng kan zumh; Nangmah lawng kan zumh ko,
   Nangmah lawng kan zumh.

[V2]
 Sual ngaih-thiamnak kha kan hal ko, Toidornak te in, Ngaih-thiamnak le
 vel-ngeihnak in, Ka pe tuah.

[C2]
   Nang kan zumh ko, Nangmah lawng kan zumh; Nangmah lawng kan zumh ko,
   Nangmah lawng kan zumh.

[V3]
 Bawipa Jesuh, ka thianter tuah, Na thi thletmi khan, Na ka thianter
 khawh lai ka zumh, Na thi in.

[C3]
   Nang kan zumh ko, Nangmah lawng kan zumh; Nangmah lawng kan zumh ko,
   Nangmah lawng kan zumh.

[V4]
 Lungchung thawnnak kan hal ko rih, Run ka pe zungzal; Na biachim awk
 na chiah vialte, Ka hngalhter.

[C4]
   Nang kan zumh ko, Nangmah lawng kan zumh; Nangmah lawng kan zumh ko,
   Nangmah lawng kan zumh.

[V5]
 Bawipa Jesuh zungzal kan duh, Ka kal tak hin hlah, Zungzal in nangmah
 kan zulh lai, Ka thih tiang.

[C5]
   Nang kan zumh ko, Nangmah lawng kan zumh; Nangmah lawng kan zumh ko,
   Nangmah lawng kan zumh.</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
<hymn_number>327</hymn_number>
</song>